{"tid":1216401,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"原來混亂中警方精神壓力大做乜都得","createTime":"2019-06-13T10:00:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T10:54:46.000Z","uid":75156,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a774b05c5bb26c9d7439c0d47ebd9b05bb28fcbd","tid":1216401,"uid":75156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:00:40.000Z","msg":"體諒wo<br />\n咁我都唔知我精神狀態不穩情況下會做乜啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da44232ea6fc07e6efe154c1b1e9f4cae085f7b2","tid":1216401,"uid":226955,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:01:37.000Z","msg":"壓力太大要爆啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LUxq7VC.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLUxq7VC.gif&h=721ac9a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>一名少年於金鐘一帶背向警察站立，遭十多名速龍小隊成員<span style=\"color: red;\">強行拉扯到地上用警棍圍毆</span>。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aQu85Ja.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaQu85Ja.gif&h=0ec58946&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>一名少女下午於立法會地下門外落單，遭近十名警員<span style=\"color: red;\">以盾牌及警棍按倒地上瘋狂圍毆</span>。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wk41Gxi.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwk41Gxi.gif&h=5c8616cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>一名手無寸鐵市民於大會堂對出方向，遭4-5名警員<span style=\"color: red;\">揮棍不停攻擊頭部倒地。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/4g17BRj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4g17BRj.gif&h=509faf8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>一名外藉男子於愛丁堡廣場附近，因行動不便獨自坐於花槽旁，<span style=\"color: red;\">遭警員以胡椒噴劑近距離向臉部射擊。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eLz5ovx.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeLz5ovx.gif&h=58851dc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i8PQzCe.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi8PQzCe.gif&h=58a9a71f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UvSnqJW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUvSnqJW.gif&h=c1469b1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>下午時份於金鐘天橋附近一帶，一名中年婦人向警員哭求停止對香港人使用武力，<span style=\"color: red;\">遭警員近距離以不明武器擊中頭部。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/d6KQzNf.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd6KQzNf.gif&h=b3ebd9eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>一名市民於金鐘橋底下，遭警員<span style=\"color: red;\">以布袋彈瞄準頭部射擊</span>。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同場加映：<br />\n示威者吐血<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hRCPds07zSM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhRCPds07zSM&d=BSpFugi7VYdA%2F48z81zRmUwFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=0878b487\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hRCPds07zSM</a> <br />\n<br />\n拖行暈倒示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GfhHJqNVPig\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGfhHJqNVPig&d=BSpFugi7VYdA%2F48z81zRmUwFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=4aea8d3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GfhHJqNVPig</a> <br />\n<br />\n唔比救護車入<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mT8SH2EJctk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmT8SH2EJctk&d=BSpFugi7VYdA%2F48z81zRmUwFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=0c2b85c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mT8SH2EJctk</a> <br />\n<br />\n地鐵站噴椒<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sQk9mLw07WM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsQk9mLw07WM&d=BSpFugi7VYdA%2F48z81zRmUwFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=77f4df4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sQk9mLw07WM</a> <br />\n<br />\n開槍<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9bbFANmVWZ4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9bbFANmVWZ4&d=BSpFugi7VYdA%2F48z81zRmUwFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=61216daf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9bbFANmVWZ4</a> <br />\n<br />\n向記者放tear gas<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cWZ0R67V5Yg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcWZ0R67V5Yg&d=BSpFugi7VYdA%2F48z81zRmUwFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=3a48cbb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cWZ0R67V5Yg</a> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">強烈建議歐美向對示威者施過度武力嘅警察懲處！終生不得踏入歐美國家半步！呢班人渣注定世世代代共享中國人嘅榮耀</span></span>"},{"pid":"e05b74fc24cebb90bce2639f95bfeca0b86a0fd4","tid":1216401,"uid":11818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a774b05c5bb26c9d7439c0d47ebd9b05bb28fcbd","tid":1216401,"uid":75156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:00:40.000Z","msg":"體諒wo<br />\n咁我都唔知我精神狀態不穩情況下會做乜啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:03:14.000Z","msg":"應該得白卡佬同佢打係公平"},{"pid":"8ff0e77db07c5d23b068d08005f6ff4076aa4f66","tid":1216401,"uid":75156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e05b74fc24cebb90bce2639f95bfeca0b86a0fd4","tid":1216401,"uid":11818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a774b05c5bb26c9d7439c0d47ebd9b05bb28fcbd","tid":1216401,"uid":75156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:00:40.000Z","msg":"體諒wo<br />\n咁我都唔知我精神狀態不穩情況下會做乜啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:03:14.000Z","msg":"應該得白卡佬同佢打係公平"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:04:00.000Z","msg":"有咩分別<br />\n白卡佬同警犬犯法都唔撚洗坐監"},{"pid":"48fe44bf540548bb0d81b536b84c833a165190f4","tid":1216401,"uid":33984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:04:05.000Z","msg":"體你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmo